{"tid":2426682,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"擄獲TWICE的小女孩長大了！ARIN初戀美貌似秀智，拍畫報展清新嫵媚魅力","createTime":"2021-02-28T09:11:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T05:23:46.000Z","uid":231132,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa9f333e7ba09ce4bcce05b527162861543db526","tid":2426682,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:11:08.000Z","msg":"韓國女團Oh My Girl自出演競演型綜藝節《Queendom》後，人氣看漲，其中年紀最小的老么成員Arin也憑藉著清新甜美的外貌擄獲粉絲的心，還曾打敗最美偶像Irene、人間香奈兒Jennie拿下韓國女團個人評價排行榜冠軍。擁有清新甜美的Arin近日為《DAZED》拍攝時尚大片，身穿多雙ASICS鞋款，展現清新俏皮、俐落等不同魅力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ljz3Mct.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLjz3Mct.jpg&h=531b84ef&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRsH1LO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRsH1LO.jpg&h=0b5b8eb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1999年出生的Arin，自出到以來就因可愛的模樣吸引許多粉絲，就連人氣偶像 TWICE、HANI都曾公開表示自己是她的粉絲。隨著年齡的增長，Arin也從當年的可愛少女變成散發出清純仙氣的初戀系女神，甚至有網友認為Arin眉宇間與國民初戀秀智有幾分神似。這次她為時尚雜誌《DAZED》韓國版拍攝畫報，以多套不同風格的造型入鏡，其中包括素面黑色洋裝、綠色背心短裙、牛仔套裝、灰白俐落褲裝、綠色西裝等，透過多套極具春夏感的穿搭，展現出兩種截然不同的魅力。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M5FOcSO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM5FOcSO.jpg&h=a2f780f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ygsH1L8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FygsH1L8.jpg&h=b4e7dea8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其中最令人印象深刻的造型就是素面黑色禮服、綠色背心短裙。照片中，Arin身穿素面黑色禮服，搭配一頭浪漫微卷的中分長髮、朦朧的眼神，散發出她獨有的小女人式的嫵媚感，讓人一看就驚艷。而綠色背心短裙造型則充分展現了少女俏麗感，但裙襬下隱約露出白皙美腿、絕對領域，還是讓整個畫面不失性感氛圍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AESEx2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AESEx2.jpg&h=bee0dbd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLjvrc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLjvrc2.jpg&h=03fd2d93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之前，Arin也曾登上時尚雜誌《Esquire》，當時Arin以極具秋季唯美風格的大地色系造型入鏡，搭配清新淡雅的妝容展現出不同以往的優雅氣質，展現不同以往的知性成熟的面貌，令人讚嘆不已。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2ZTToZS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2ZTToZS.jpg&h=c7f0ca73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fOcEyc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fOcEyc.jpg&h=a1483365&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39cbbde81704cec8af7544ad8ca8ef1df6189dee","tid":2426682,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />超正式。。"},{"pid":"2ea219c315048fc3f0023bf8ca9f9225dea5a400","tid":2426682,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:15:31.000Z","msg":"勁靚靚..."},{"pid":"dbe946468fc700f09cc64e446f63d87d173eec98","tid":2426682,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"衰妹終於大個女，可以同我一齊做成人的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0bc68b1a5e9db988a469a81336c5b5a0fc8437","tid":2426682,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"Arin超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9830628c25e9fc2fa5f862e12f4255bf3d11260a","tid":2426682,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbe946468fc700f09cc64e446f63d87d173eec98","tid":2426682,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:17:35.000Z","msg":"衰妹終於大個女，可以同我一齊做成人的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T09:39:46.000Z","msg":"on9...？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e8d3e8b2cc8d448dcae95a054b3acac9108ab8","tid":2426682,"uid":136770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbe946468fc700f09cc64e446f63d87d173eec98","tid":2426682,"uid":235015,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedB